1. Resolved: AC-013, AC-013b, and AC-019 now share one keyed `DEVLOOP_NUMBERS` contract through the single `emit_numbers()` helper, so the field set and order are identical across all three ACs. AC-019-specific extras moved to a separate `DEVLOOP_AC019_DETAIL` line. Refs: [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:175), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:291), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:361), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:456), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:458), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:133), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:136).

2. Resolved: code and doc now agree that cold-cache real runs are allowed, and nothing in the test enforces a warm-cache precondition. Cache state is reported via `cache=...`; the real path’s latency remains report-only. Refs: [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:48), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:105), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:160), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:303), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:48), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:87), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:110).

3. Resolved: the real-path latency comment is now accurate. Warmup and measure both call `engine.search()`, `search()` still invokes the embedder on every query, and the harness embedder caches embeddings in memory, so the measure pass is embed-cache-warm rather than “live candle inference”; the recall ground-truth path uses a fresh real embedder, so it does re-embed live. Refs: [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:293), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:320), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:88), [lib.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:1915), [corpus_harness.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/support/corpus_harness.rs:432), [corpus_harness.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/support/corpus_harness.rs:624).

Regression checks also look intact. The synthetic default path still owns the catastrophic ceiling and would RED-show the scanner regression ([perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:115), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:300), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:47)); the structural asserts still guard batch-collapse ([perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:258), [corpus_harness.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/support/corpus_harness.rs:388)); and there is no production read-path bypass because all passes still drive `engine.search()` end-to-end while only embeddings, not results, are cached ([perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:279), [perf_gates_devloop.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/perf_gates_devloop.rs:428), [lib.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:1942), [corpus_harness.rs](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/tests/support/corpus_harness.rs:486), [perf-gates.md](/home/coreyt/projects/fathomdb/dev/design/perf-gates.md:96)).
